quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  20,55,Ex it nos created vos it nos return vos ex it nos bring vos out dodum multus
  20,56,Nos showed eum totus noster proofs he disbelieved refused
  20,57,He dictus vos advenit hic take nos noster terra tuus magic O Moses
  20,58,Nos surely show vos similar magic Ergo set appointment ut nec nos nor vos violate; neutral locus
  20,59,He dictus Tuus appointed temporis est feria festivities. all meet forenoon
  20,60,Pharaoh summoned his forces tunc advenit
  20,61,Moses dictus to them Woe to vos. Vos fabricate lies fight DEUS perfecit ergo incur His retribution? Such fabricators surely fail
  20,62,They disputed themselves prout they conferred privately
  20,63,They dictus These 2 est non multus than magicians wish take vos tuus terra their magic to destroy tuus ideal via de vita
  20,64,agree upon 1 scheme face them prout united front winner hodie habet superior manus
  20,65,They dictus O Moses either vos throw nos est primus throw
  20,66,He dictus Vos throw Whereupon their ropes sticks comparuit eum their magic prout they moving
  20,67,Moses harbored some fear
  20,68,Nos dictus non Habet fear Vos prevail
  20,69,Throw quod vos habuit in tuus rectus manus it swallow quod they fabricated quod they fabricated est non multus than scheming magician. magician's work non succeed
  20,70,magicians fell prostrate dictus Nos believe in Dominus de Aaron Moses
  20,71,He dictus Perfecit vos believe in eum my disponsationis? He est tuus chief unus taught vos magic Ego surely sever tuus manus feet alternate sides Ego crucify vos palm trunks Vos perfecit invenit out quae de nos inflict male retribution qui outlasts whom
  20,72,They dictus Nos non prefer vos clear proofs ut advenit nos ac Unus created nos! Ergo proles whatever judgment vos wish proles! Vos unus dominus in hoc humilis vita
  20,73,Nos habet believed in noster Dominus ut He forgive nos noster sins magic ut vos forced nos perform DEUS est far BENE Everlasting
  20,74,Anyone advenit his Dominus guilty testimentum incur Hell wherein he nunquam abiit nor stays alive
  20,75,Prout pro those advenit Eum believers led righteous vita they attain high ranks
